<item>
            <title>[HIVE-111] join without a ON clause dies</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-111</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;join without a ON clause dies&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For eg: the following query:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;select x.* from x JOIN y&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;results in a null pointer exception.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should be treated as a cartesian product&lt;/p&gt;</description>
